### ProjectFlow API Tests
### Use REST Client extension in VSCode

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@contentType = application/json

### Variables (update after login)
@sessionToken = your-session-token-here

###############################################
# Authentication Tests
###############################################

### 1. Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "sakonpalliative@gmail.com",
  "password": "your-password"
}

### 2. Get Current User (requires auth)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{sessionToken}}

### 3. Logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{sessionToken}}

###############################################
# Tasks Tests
###############################################

### 4. Get All Tasks
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{sessionToken}}

### 5. Get Tasks by Project
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks?projectId=your-project-id
Authorization: Bearer {{sessionToken}}

### 6. Get Tasks with Filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks?isClosed=false&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{sessionToken}}

###############################################
# Health Check (if needed)
###############################################

### 7. Check if API is running
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health
